{"tid":1807180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日風向:blame the victim, blame the 勇武","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:57:40.000Z","uid":258649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60c6a7e7655631c3d40536f8d53b23c24c9b90b1","tid":1807180,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"因為勇武蠢,所以搞到全世界冇得行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明明勇武都想繼續行落去,都想人數靚D好睇D<br />\n叫人散,射人TG係班狗,唔係勇武<br />\n然後個個係度BLAME THE VICTIM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個二個為左人數屌黎屌去<br />\n民陣都講左人數已經唔再重要<br />\n有張相畀外國睇就得啦<br />\n<br />\n幫人裝修要搵命博架,事前要買幾多GEAR做幾多準備<br />\n唔係暖氣軍師講一兩句就得<br />\n仲要諗過幾多個夜晚先有心理準備夠膽落手<br />\n<br />\n最後我希望各位可以多謝今日既勇武,冇佢地班狗實發癲未散就狂射TG狂推進<br />\n冇佢地,送中條例過左啦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n多謝勇武</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話:<br />\n我覺得捉唔捉鬼係要拎一個平衡點<br />\n無理由見佢拎住支槍扑中銀你都唔捉架<br />\n但同時有D阿姐阿叔唔知係咪睇太多FB見到人扑就話係鬼<br />\nCHECK都唔FACT就上前打勇武,到個陣真係要人幫下手調解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198dbfb254c198fedccdcdc4e29675f213af6abd","tid":1807180,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT